<template>
  <NewMessage/>
</template>

<script>

import NewMessage from "@/components/NewMessage"


const getPokemonData = async query => {

    const url = `https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokemon?limit=100000&offset=0${query}`
    const response = await fetch(url)

    // if (response.status == 404 || response.statusText == 'Not Found') {
    // }

    const pokemon = response.json()
    console.log('getPokemonData сработала')
    return pokemon
}

export default {
  name: 'App',
  components: {
    NewMessage
  },
  data() {
    return {
      pokemons : getPokemonData()
    }
  }
}
</script>
